room_title: Escape room "The Billionaire's Den" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
room_address: 840 1st Avenue, Suite 500 King of Prussia, PA 19406
room_description: Your rich great uncle was always bugging you to come over for family game night in his eccentric den.  Now that he has passed away, his will dictates that you play his crazy games in order to inherit his billions! Can you unravel the puzzles your uncle has prepared to receive your inheritance?
